law.history: Repealed 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 118, sec. 19. -- Amended 1972, sec. 203, sec. 47. --Amended 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 119, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 913-1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: County may contract with city, county, city-county board of health or private hospital for hospitalization of indigent residents -- Reimbursement for emergency care.
